  <!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0"/>
  <title>For Nitika 💖</title>
  <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>

  <style>
    body {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #ff9a9e, #fad0c4);
    }
    .slide { display: none; }
    .active { display: block; }
  </style>
</head>

<body class="min-h-screen flex items-center justify-center px-4">

<div class="bg-white shadow-2xl rounded-2xl p-6 max-w-md w-full text-center">

  <!-- SLIDE 1 -->
  <div class="slide active">
    <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold text-pink-500 mb-4">💖 Happy 2 Months 💖</h1>
    <p>Tap next… I made something for you 💖</p>
    <button onclick="nextSlide()" class="btn">Next ➡️</button>
  </div>

  <!-- SLIDE 2 -->
  <div class="slide">
    <p>
      Nitika Tomar… oops 😅 Nitika Verma ❤️
    </p>
    <button onclick="nextSlide()" class="btn">Next ➡️</button>
  </div>

  <!-- SLIDE 3 -->
  <div class="slide">
    <p>
      We met in university… you were my senior,
      and I had no idea you would become this important to me.
    </p>
    <button onclick="nextSlide()" class="btn">Next ➡️</button>
  </div>

  <!-- SLIDE 4 -->
  <div class="slide">
    <p>
      I approached you first… and you didn’t say yes 😅
      but I’m really glad you finally did 💕
    </p>
    <button onclick="nextSlide()" class="btn">Next ➡️</button>
  </div>

  <!-- SLIDE 5 -->
  <div class="slide">
    <p>
      These 2 months with you have been
      the most beautiful part of my life 💖
    </p>
    <button onclick="nextSlide()" class="btn">Next ➡️</button>
  </div>

  <!-- SLIDE 6 -->
  <div class="slide">
    <p>
      You became my peace, my happiness,
      and my safe place 🌸
    </p>
    <button onclick="nextSlide()" class="btn">Next ➡️</button>
  </div>

  <!-- SLIDE 7 -->
  <div class="slide">
    <p>
      That day… when we sat together,
      eating ice cream 🍦
      It was simple… but one of my favorite memories ever ✨
    </p>
    <button onclick="nextSlide()" class="btn">Next ➡️</button>
  </div>

  <!-- SLIDE 8 -->
  <div class="slide">
    <p>
      Honestly… I don’t want anyone else but you 💖
    </p>
    <button onclick="nextSlide()" class="btn">Next ➡️</button>
  </div>

  <!-- SLIDE 9 -->
  <div class="slide">
    <p>
      If you weren’t in my life,
      maybe I would still feel alone…
      but you changed everything 💫
    </p>
    <button onclick="nextSlide()" class="btn">Next ➡️</button>
  </div>

  <!-- SLIDE 10 (PHOTOS + FINAL LINE) -->
  <div class="slide">
    <h2 class="text-xl text-pink-500 mb-3">Our Moments 💞</h2>

    <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-2 mb-4">
      <img src="img1.jpg" class="rounded-xl"/>
      <img src="img2.jpg" class="rounded-xl"/>
      <img src="img3.jpg" class="rounded-xl"/>
      <img src="img4.jpg" class="rounded-xl"/>
    </div>

    <p class="text-purple-600 font-semibold">
      Listen baby u heal me bache ❤️
    </p>
  </div>

</div>

<script>
  let current = 0;
  const slides = document.querySelectorAll(".slide");

  function nextSlide() {
    slides[current].classList.remove("active");
    current++;
    if (current < slides.length) {
      slides[current].classList.add("active");
    }
  }
</script>

<style>
  .btn {
    margin-top: 20px;
    padding: 10px 20px;
    background: #ec4899;
    color: white;
    border-radius: 12px;
  }
</style>

</body>
</html>
